    <string name="onboard_4_title">One master switch</string>
    <string name="onboard_4_body">At the top of the main screen. Leave it on so rules apply while you use other apps.</string>
    <string name="onboard_4_enforce_title">Enforce rules</string>
    <string name="onboard_4_enforce_body">On = apply per-app rules. Off = pause and restore system rotation.</string>
    <string name="onboard_4_modes_title">Modes at a glance</string>
    <string name="onboard_4_modes_body">• Landscape / Portrait — lock a fixed orientation\n• Auto (sensor) — follow tilt (lock icon freezes angle)\n• System default — no override</string>
